OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1778929376
OL,3,CSacks of roofing materials fly tipped
OL,4,Cin rural Dorset
OL,6,FDorset Council is investigating after
OL,7,Fsacks of roofing materials were dumped
OL,8,Fin rural parts of the county.
OL,10,FThe waste was dumped in red sacks in
OL,11,Ftwo areas of Dorset, causing damage to
OL,12,Fthe local environment and creating
OL,13,Fhazards for walkers and horse riders.
OL,15,FThe first incident took place near
OL,16,FGales Hill, Cosmore, at the end of
OL,17,FMarch.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
