PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1778929376
OL,3,CSacks of roofing materials fly tipped
OL,4,Cin rural Dorset
OL,6,FA second flytip was discovered during
OL,7,Fthe weekend of 9/10 May near Zig Zag
OL,8,FHill, near Shaftesbury.JDorset Council
OL,9,Fsay they are carrying out
OL,10,Finvestigations to trace those
OL,11,Fresponsible.
OL,13,FThey want to hear from anyone who may
OL,14,Fhave seen roofing work being carried
OL,15,Fout in the area, vehicles transporting
OL,16,Froofing waste, or suspicious activity
OL,17,Fnear the affected bridleways around
OL,18,Fthe times of the incidents.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
