CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1778929376
OL,3,CSacks of roofing materials fly tipped
OL,4,Cin rural Dorset
OL,6,FThey are also keen to see dashcam
OL,7,Ffootage, doorstep video or details
OL,8,Fsuch as a vehicle description, a
OL,9,Fpartial car registration number
OL,10,Fplates, company name, times and
OL,11,Flocations could help officers identify
OL,12,Fthose responsible.
OL,14,FCllr Jon Andrews, Cabinet Member for
OL,15,FPlace Services, said:
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
