FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1778929376
OL,3,CSacks of roofing materials fly tipped
OL,4,Cin rural Dorset
OL,6,F"Flytipping is selfish, illegal and
OL,7,Fcompletely unacceptable. It damages
OL,8,FDorset's beautiful countryside,
OL,9,Fcreates real problems for people who
OL,10,Fuse and care for our bridleways and
OL,11,Fcosts taxpayers thousands of pounds in
OL,12,Fclear-up fees.
OL,14,F"If you've seen roofing work taking
OL,15,Fplace nearby, noticed vehicles dumping
OL,16,Fwaste, or have any information that
OL,17,Fcould help our investigation, please
OL,18,Fget in touch. It will be treated in
OL,19,Fstrict confidence but could make a
OL,20,Freal difference.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
