OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1778929376
OL,3,CSacks of roofing materials fly tipped
OL,4,Cin rural Dorset
OL,6,F"We are committed to protecting the
OL,7,Fcounty's natural environment and will
OL,8,Ftake enforcement action against those
OL,9,Fresponsible for fly tipping."
OL,11,FAnyone with information is asked to
OL,12,Fcontact Dorset Council on 01305
OL,13,F221000. All information provided will
OL,14,Fbe treated in strict confidence.
OL,16,FBusinesses, including traders carrying
OL,17,Fout work for households, must dispose
OL,18,Fof their waste using licensed
OL,19,Fcommercial waste facilities.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@]O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
