CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1778929376
OL,3,CSacks of roofing materials fly tipped
OL,4,Cin rural Dorset
OL,6,FThis must be done either by arranging
OL,7,Fcollections with a licensed waste
OL,8,Fcarrier or by taking waste directly to
OL,9,Fa licensed commercial waste site or
OL,10,Ftransfer station.
OL,12,FHousehold recycling centres cannot be
OL,13,Flegally used for business or trade
OL,14,Fwaste.
OL,16,FIf waste is fly tipped and traced back
OL,17,Fto a household, the householder can
OL,18,Fface enforcement action, including
OL,19,Ffines, even if the waste was dumped by
OL,20,Fa contractor.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
